                    "body": "Please grab the generated markup, and post it to the Dojo mailing lists and\/or bug tracker. Unfortunately, we cannot support Dojo-specific issues, only issues that are specific to the Zend Framework Dojo integration (i.e., creating invalid markup and\/or JS).",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=matthew",
                        "name": "matthew",
                        "displayName": "Matthew Weier O'Phinney",
